  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "Indexed\n63-2013\nD-5\n\nHerb Asher is not H. Fat; Emmanuel is (H. Fat), + look who Emmanuel is (but has forgotten)! YHWH. Good Lord. All 3 books tell the same story: H. Fat, Emmanuel + Bill/Tim are God/Christ. Talk about \"personal transcendence with religious overtones\" as Tom Disch says! Christ, forgetful + confused + entranced + in thrall by/to the info life form (plasmate, Satan). So Satan did claim the sacrifice, the lamb; the Manichaean story of the defeat + swallowing of primal man by darknes",
      "matched_alias": "Asher",
      "term_id": "TERM_asher",
      "term_name": "Asher",
      "term_slug": "asher"
    }
  ],
